Package meico.mei

Contains the MEI class and a Helper class that is mostly used for MEI processing but offers some useful functionality also for other datatypes such as MSM and MPM.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributesWithIds
    This is a helper class for method Mei.resolveCopyofs().
    Helper
    This class is used for mei to msm conversion to hold temporary data, used in class Mei.
    Mei
    This class holds the mei data from a source file in a XOM Document.
    Mei2MsmMpmConverter
    This class does the MEI to MSM/MPM conversion.
    Mei2MusicXmlConverter
    This class does the conversion from MEI to MusicXML.

Package meico.mei Description

Contains the MEI class and a Helper class that is mostly used for MEI processing but offers some useful functionality also for other datatypes such as MSM and MPM.
